{"tid":2436560,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"劉兆佳：，支持政府搞既得利益者（業主？）令社會更公平","createTime":"2021-03-07T08:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T03:06:24.000Z","uid":24730,"like":22,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"3d177225689fb367ed23f9fe1ba369e5c336e02b","tid":2436560,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T08:37:36.000Z","msg":"韓正強調房屋問題係香港深層矛盾，並指整頓完選舉制度就會處理樓市後，劉兆佳隨即表態支持政府採取可能觸及既得利益者嘅改革，令社會更公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首候選人689聽到韓正咁講，佢或佢班炮兵（張志剛、白宮發言人、屈婦人...）近期一定會炮轟樓市，而柒婆為咗不落人後，又會趁快出下招打壓下樓市。成個建制派都會寧左勿右，準備入市嘅人睇路！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n★劉兆佳：深層次矛盾改革的目標，可能觸及既得利益者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2436290\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2436290</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d6ca59c033edda86b2a75548b38c89887aa04fd3","tid":2436560,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377ea2ef1e484c908a9b564998211b08e26f36eb","tid":2436560,"uid":56537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass